r />\n唔怕誤中就嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffec56fff8825e93c177194f309b4c3acac7e9ef","tid":766391,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"邪惡軸心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b82c0f98cfb29af047a2e6bb8e118b2a387fd3","tid":766391,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c737f6155e8472d32019d53e4cda958476561bb0","tid":766391,"uid":24140,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"524247df49780f9dff0ecdbb04145683b6e3b57a","tid":766391,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"出兵轉移國內視線？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"最主要係為Uyghurs 而出動<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2c/Kokbayraq_flag.svg/640px-Kokbayraq_flag.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F2%2F2c%2FKokbayraq_flag.svg%2F640px-Kokbayraq_flag.svg.png&h=a824d505&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"佢地要快 D 輸出革命去東突厥斯坦先得架"},{"pid":"e409852d8a5256baa07f84f58bb96c504d405aff","tid":766391,"uid":140928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:13:51.000Z","msg":"人地差唔多打完先出黎執尾刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63cc91df5392e169cc7cc2deba56054afd8af39","tid":766391,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"據報導，中國駐大馬士革大使告訴敘利亞媒體，北京準備幫助政府推動重新奪回全國各地。<br />\n<br />\n根據中東媒體研究所的一份報告，特使齊千金在敘利亞親政府日報Al-Watan的講話中表示，中國支持他所謂的敘利亞反恐戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n齊說他很遺憾中國維吾爾人參加了巴沙爾&middot;阿薩德總統的政府鬥爭，並表示中國軍方希望加強與敘利亞軍隊的關係。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;當被問及他的國家是否有可能參加敘利亞阿拉伯軍隊即將開展的反對伊德利卜恐怖主義分子的運動時，尤其是考慮到維吾爾族戰士的存在，[齊]回答說，中國正在關注敘利亞局勢特別是在南部[敘利亞]取得勝利之後，其軍隊願意與敘利亞軍隊並肩作戰，與敘利亞任何其他地區的恐怖分子作戰，&ldquo;Al-Watan的文章被翻譯成了如上所述。<br />\n<br />\n當被問及中國參與這項運動時，軍事專員Wong Roy Chang說：&ldquo;敘利亞和中國軍隊之間的軍事合作正在進行中。我們有良好的關係，我們保持這種合作，以服務於我們各國的安全，正直和穩定。我們 - 中國及其軍隊 - 希望發展與敘利亞軍隊的關係。至於參與伊德利卜行動，需要做出政治決定。&ldquo;他否認今天在敘利亞有軍事顧問或特種中國軍隊。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"dfd77910cd0df8e8b195f0ea075e84f0cbfdad72","tid":766391,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf14746a25b6922212856500d017961d9689cf75","tid":766391,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:27:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38ba701bed66050b752ae5e987b7026382104bb1","tid":766391,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你差隻腳走去做豬隊友"},{"pid":"cc2843eb9479a028ad8ea394358d2bbc11f8896e","tid":766391,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e409852d8a5256baa07f84f58bb96c504d405aff","tid":766391,"uid":140928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:13:51.000Z","msg":"人地差唔多打完先出黎執尾刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:31:50.000Z","msg":"「賊過興兵」既完美示範"},{"pid":"d8f129a185e21f855eb31da9631335b479c80506","tid":766391,"uid":112935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"大陸玩唔玩得起敍利亞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b7f4118511b016e87f7fc9b744f79111afe5e8","tid":766391,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"得邪惡國家先支持敍利亞政權, 支那一撐連左膠都反埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4d7da378bc61007531f7a475c3a17f7db87cfb","tid":766391,"uid":48767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:41:48.000Z","msg":"2012<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"